{"title":"数十年如一日","authors":["易和元","王复羊"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":4,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"数十年如一日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易和元 诗 王复羊 画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我是大老粗，外行！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"余音袅袅，意味深长："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既象是表示谦虚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又象是自我欣赏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年岁岁花相似，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁岁年年话一样："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我是大老粗，外行！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面盾牌老挂在嘴上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心满意足，甘作外行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自个儿把双脚捆绑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大好时光等闲度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耽误了自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"损害了党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志，劝你要认真想一想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老调子千万不能再唱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要只争朝夕变内行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新长征途上贡献力量！（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}